@startuml
title 分布式锁一期核心角色关系图

interface DistributedLockClient
interface LockHandle
class DefaultDistributedLockClient
class DefaultLockHandle
class LockOptions
class LockResult
class LockLease
class LockRuntimeState
interface LockProvider
class RedisLockProvider
interface LockWaiter
class NoWaitLockWaiter
class BackoffLockWaiter
interface LockWatchdog
class ScheduledLockWatchdog
class OwnerTokenGenerator
class LockEventPublisher
class LockMetricsRecorder

DistributedLockClient <|.. DefaultDistributedLockClient
LockHandle <|.. DefaultLockHandle
LockProvider <|.. RedisLockProvider
LockWatchdog <|.. ScheduledLockWatchdog

DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockOptions
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockResult
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> OwnerTokenGenerator
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockWaiter
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockProvider
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockWatchdog
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockEventPublisher
DefaultDistributedLockClient --> LockMetricsRecorder

DefaultLockHandle --> LockLease
DefaultLockHandle --> LockRuntimeState
DefaultLockHandle --> LockProvider
DefaultLockHandle --> LockEventPublisher

RedisLockProvider --> LockLease

note right of DistributedLockClient
  业务入口。
  提供 tryLock 和 execute。
end note

note right of DefaultDistributedLockClient
  核心编排器。
  负责校验、加锁、执行 callback、
  release、watchdog、事件、指标。
end note

note right of DefaultLockHandle
  一次锁租约的操作句柄。
  负责 unlock / renew / checkHeld。
end note

note bottom of LockLease
  不可变租约快照。
  描述这次锁是谁拿到的。
end note

note bottom of LockRuntimeState
  JVM 内部运行态。
  lost / released。
end note

@enduml